    "/home/michael/prj/nu-agent/README.md",
    "9bf89275e5d523de4b5dc5c1c2ea5deb36f70fb54d700a8a9b969f715696e40d",
    nu-agent,
    [
      Files
    ],
    "Core agent surface:
``mod.nu``
 ŌĆö thin aggregator that re-exports the public commands (
``airun``
, 
``run-json``
, 
``enrich``
) and canonical tools.
``agent/runtime.nu``
 ŌĆö builds tool schemas at runtime, validates model output, and executes whitelisted commands.
``agent/schema.nu``
 ŌĆö inspects Nushell command signatures and enforces the whitelist/argument contract.
``agent/llm.nu``
 ŌĆö JSON-only response parsing and repair around the LLM API.
``agent/enrichment.nu``
 ŌĆö single-record enrichment entrypoint and schema validation.
``agent/json.nu``
 ŌĆö shared JSON helpers used by multiple layers.
``api.nu``
 ŌĆö 
``http post``
 wrapper with strict no-prose system prompt.
``tools.nu``
 ŌĆö canonical Nushell tools plus the single-source 
``TOOL_REGISTRY``
 metadata.
Optional retrieval tooling (not required for the agent runtime):
``scripts/ingest-docs.nu``
 ŌĆö wraps shredding, command-map generation, and embedding production into a single command.
``scripts/make-data-from-chunks.nu``
 ŌĆö normalises shredder output into the 
``data/``
 and 
``build/nu_ingest/``
 stores used by the tools.
``target/debug/embed_runner``
, 
``target/debug/nu-search``
 ŌĆö binaries built from 
``crates/nu_plugin_rag``
 that generate deterministic embeddings and let you smoke-test similarity search.
See 
``docs/RAG_HAPPY_PATH.md``
 for an end-to-end walkthrough of the current pipeline.
Reference docs:
``RULES.md``
 ŌĆö hard project constraints.
``PLAN.md``
 ŌĆö current status and next steps.
",
