 ŌĆö inspects Nushell command signatures and enforces the whitelist/argument contract.
``agent/llm.nu``
 ŌĆö JSON-only response parsing and repair around the LLM API.
``agent/enrichment.nu``
 ŌĆö single-record enrichment entrypoint and schema validation.
``agent/json.nu``
 ŌĆö shared JSON helpers used by multiple layers.
